body_html: Try checking out the version of mnist_softmax.py at the branch of the version you have installed. E.g., if you have r0.11 installed, check out the version of mnist_softmax.py in the r0.11 branch of git. That should hopefully solve your problems. Please ping this thread if you feel there's something more to this.
